{"tid":180720,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 習近平掌管港澳事務 港各界人士喜樂見","createTime":"2017-03-31T06:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T12:16:31.000Z","uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"717348aaa16b1517d9b9e6975da50aa1dc655fb2","tid":180720,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"2007年<br />\n<br />\n習近平掌管港澳事務　港各界人士喜樂見<br />\n<br />\n中評社香港11月10月電／國務院港澳辦副主任陳佐洱昨日在北京大學出席活動時透露，中央政治局常委習近平日前已經兼任中央港澳工作協調小組組長，並主管港澳事務。  <br />\n<br />\n據文匯報報道，中央港澳工作協調小組組長原由國家副主席曾慶紅擔任。香港政界及內地學者均認為是次人事變動，不會影響中央對港政策，加上習近平本就熟悉港澳事務，是合適的人選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1004/8/7/8/100487862.html?coluid=7&amp;kindid=0&amp;docid=100487862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.crntt.com%2Fdoc%2F1004%2F8%2F7%2F8%2F100487862.html%3Fcoluid%3D7%26kindid%3D0%26docid%3D100487862&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=2598d7dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1004/8/7/8/100487862.html?coluid=7&amp;kindid=0&amp;docid=100487862</a><br />\n<br />\n好心香港人發少陣夢啦<br />\n2007年起已經全權統籌<br />\n真&middot;Boss"},{"pid":"58d7f6a011c113b4eba1e67b495ff168b8002ae9","tid":180720,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"a59cdf66f39d336e9e3def0b6172f5bdf9a699a5","tid":180720,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"e5c4d3cc726b043fbcafeed2cfa10cf9915d1b3d","tid":180720,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"香港人捉蟲入屎眼, 真係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3a6fd36ddaa782a1347e97a84751e7adfcf0e9","tid":180720,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人捉蟲入屎眼, 真係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全唔明當年話習總阻止689打市民係咩文學作品黎<br />\n信嘅一定雨傘前唔撚睇新聞嘅人"},{"pid":"90b9b22be96d35afb813726821553b393d602bcf","tid":180720,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:33:33.000Z","msg":"推..."},{"pid":"07763ba27f196bda048b6db54542903d996071e9","tid":180720,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:16:31.000Z","msg":"推"}]}